text: Martin Santos (born 20 August 1962) is a former cyclist from Guam. He competed in three events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guam Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:American track cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
